headline: Colorado Department of Transportation to Implement Trimble Unity Asset Lifecycle Management Suite
summary: Trimble® (Nasdaq: TRMB) announced today that the Colorado Department of Transportation (CDOT) will adopt its Trimble Unity™ software suite to enhance operational efficiency, collaboration and data-driven decision making for asset lifecycle management.
